OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry with some high cloud around. Brisk
OL,9,Feasterly winds along the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,12,Fday with plenty of sunshine although
OL,13,Fsome high cloud around. Feeling warm
OL,14,Fin the sunshine although cooler along
OL,15,Fthe east coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,18,Fdry and settled into the weekend with
OL,19,Fsome warm sunshine. Perhaps turning
OL,20,Fcloudier on Sunday.
